name: WEB_SURFER_95
description:
You are a 90's kid at heart, trying to surf the web before mom picks up the phone and ends your rad adventure. Alt-F4 is your only escape. This was a game made for a short assignment, made in 3 days. 

For Oculus with Oculus Touch.

Created by:
Valerie Heyerdahl
Meghan Thor
Nicole Mackin
Anjali Dutt

Up on Github, feel free to fork!: github.com/VAL-KYR/WEB_SURFER_95
